Text: eBay RegistrationPST Dear Congratulations You have taken the first step to becoming a registered member of eBay Your eBay User ID is Your Confirmation code is Please note The confirmation code above is not your eBay password You will create a password by following the directions below To complete your registration and join the eBay Community click here awcgieBayISAPIdllEBayRegisterConfirmnumberemail If you have any problems with the above link to complete registration there is another way to complete your registration Simply open your web browser copy the link below into the browser and fill out the required information awcgieBayISAPIdllEBayRegisterConfirm Make sure you copy this link exactly and do not add extra spaces If you need help completing your eBay registration you can take our registration tutorial by clicking here navigatortour You can also contact eBays customer support by clicking here helpbasicsselectsupporthtml Copyright eBay Inc All Rights Reserved Designated trademarks and brands are the property of their respective owners
